\id 2JN - Baga Translation Unicode
\h 2 IsaŇč
\toc3 2SAŇä
\toc2 2 IsaŇč
\toc1 Areka Ňča m…õr…ôŇč nŇč…õ IsaŇč …õnacics…õ alaŇč m…Ē
\mt1 2 IsaŇč
\imt1 An'…Ē IsaŇč …Ēy…Ēn…õ-…õ, t'ake t…Ē p…ômar pakaraŇč…õn…õ areka Ňč…Ēn Ňča m…õr…ôŇč-…õ?
\ip IsaŇč w…ôsom w…ôka Yesu …õnacic…ôs areka Ňč…Ēn Ňča m…õr…ôŇč nŇč…õ meren w…ôco cam…ôt-maas k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt (85) k…ôb…ôp ka meren w…ôco cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt (95) nt…õ k…ôkom ka Yesu Krist k…ônacep…ôr m…Ē. IsaŇč …õnament…ôrn…õ f…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka w…ôcic…ôs ka areka ŇčaŇč…õ, mba encwen…õ nk…Ēns…ôrka ¬ęW…ôbeki¬Ľ. Moloku ma Areka Ňča m…õr…ôŇč Ňča IsaŇč m…Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…ôsur…õn…õ mm…õ amb…ôp Kawandi k…Ēn m…Ē. Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē t…õntam k…ôyi p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē oloku teta tosom ta Yesu m…Ē, a pab…Ēt…ôr…õn…õ aŇč…õ k…Ē ak…Ē. K…Ē nt…õ oloku k…ôb…Ēt…ôr ka Yesu d…ômosom m…Ē (1.5-6, IsaŇč 15.9-10). Anc…õm-c…õmn…õ a IsaŇč w…ôsom w…ôka Yesu …õnacic…ôs Kawandi k…Ēn k…Ē reka y…Ēn maas t…õm nt…õ …õnayi dare da Efesi m…Ē. IsaŇč …õnacics…õ k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč a Yesu nk…õ …õnawe ¬ęW…ôran w…ôy…õk-y…õk k…Ē awut …Ēn¬Ľ\f + \fr 1:0 \ft IsaŇč p…ôtubc…õn…õ k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč a Yesu k…Ē ¬ęw…ôran w…ôy…õk-y…õk k…Ē awut …Ēn.¬Ľ\f* m…Ē. T…õfaŇč ta IsaŇč nt…õ t…õnas…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôcic…ôs areka ŇčaŇč…õ m…Ē t…õnay…Ēn…õ k…ôyeŇčk…ôs k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč b…ôk…ôc p…ôs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôbumn…õ m…õt…ôks…õ ma yem.
\iot Tokot…ôr…õn…õ ta moloku m'areka
\io1 1. IsaŇč oncop areka p…ôcbonc ak…Ē ancic…õ Ňči m…Ē p…ôcyif…õn…õ Ňča s…Ē (1.1-3).
\io1 2. K…Ē t…õy…õf…õ d…ônda-…õ p…ôcyeŇčk…ôs k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč a Yesu b…ôk…ôc, p…ôcc…õm-c…õm…ôs Ňča s…Ē tosom t…Ēk…Ē t…õmb…õk mosom f…ôp m…Ē (1.4-6).
\io1 3. K…Ē tencep…ôr-…õ, IsaŇč oloku afum k…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ atiŇčk…ôr afum aŇč…õ Ňčander m…Ē (1.7-11).
\io1 4. K…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč a Yesu nk…õ eyi m…Ē, k'…õl…ôps…ôr k…ôyif (1.12-13).
\c 1
\s1 K…ôyif
\p 
\v 1 Ina, w…ôbeki, incic areka nŇč…õ k…ôk…Ē nda w…ôran nw…õ Kanu k…ôy…õk-y…õk m…Ē\f + \fr 1:1 \fq W…ôran nw…õ Kanu k…ôy…õk-y…õk m…Ē k…Ē awut …Ēn\ft = k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč Yesu\f* k…Ē awut …Ēn aŇč…õ imb…Ēt…ôr yati m…Ē. Baf…Ē ina sona …Ēb…Ēt…ôr nu, mba ak…Ē Ňčanc…ôr…õ kance m…Ē f…ôp.
\v 2 Imb…Ēt…ôr nu teta kance nk…õ k…ôyi su k…Ē k…ôndeyi su doru o doru m…Ē.
\v 3 Papa Kanu k…Ē Yesu Krist wan ka Papa Ňčas…ĒŇč su k…ômar kif…ôli, n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr k…Ē p…ôforu d…ôkance k…Ē d…ôk…ôb…Ēt…ôr m…Ē.
\s1 Tosom nt…õ as…Ēt…ôr Papa m…Ē
\p 
\v 4 Bel-bel b…Ē p…ômb…Ēt im k…ôb…ôp awut am al…Ēma Ňčack…Ēt…õn…õ kance, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Papa osom su ti m…Ē.
\v 5 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, m…ôna w…ôran nw…õ Kanu k…ôy…õk-y…õk m…Ē\f + \fr 1:5 \fq W…ôran nw…õ Kanu k…ôy…õk-y…õk m…Ē\ft = K…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč a Yesu. \f*, intol'am nt…õ iyi k…ôcic'am m…Ē: Pab…Ēt…ôr…õn…õ! Baf…Ē tosom tofu t…Ē, mba nt…õ s…ônas…Ēt…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôk…ôcop da k…ôlaŇč kosu m…Ē.
\v 6 K…ôb…Ēt…ôr k…ôy…Ēn…õ: P…ômar pak…Ēt mosom ma Kanu p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē k…ôloku mi m…Ē. Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ tosom nt…õ p…ômar n…ôk…Ēt m…Ē, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē n…ônane ti k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôk…ôcop da k…ôlaŇč konu m…Ē.
\p 
\v 7 AtiŇčk…ôr afum alar…ôm Ňčasams…ôr doru, Ňčafati k…ôwos…õ k…ôloku a Yesu Krist kance disr…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ fum. W…ôtiŇčk…ôr afum w…ôkak…Ē w…ôter ka Krist …Ēy…Ēn…õ.
\v 8 N…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ n…ônas…ôrka nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta yokom ya y…õb…ôc yonu y…Ēs…Ēl…ôr nu m…Ē, mba n…ôs…Ēt…Ēn…õ ti k…ôway k…ôt…ôŇčn…õn…õ ka ti.
\p 
\v 9 M…ôna nw…õ o nw…õ …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôb…Ēl…õ, mba ta m…ôyi k…ôt…ôks…õ ka Krist m…Ē, m…ôy…Ē f…õ Kanu. M…ôna nw…õ m…ôŇčyi k…ôt…ôks…õ kaŇčk…Ē disr…õ m…Ē, m…ôy…Ē Kas k…Ē Wan.
\v 10 K…Ē fum ender p…ôy'un dac…Ē mba ta …õŇčk…õr…õ k…ôt…ôks…õ kaŇčk…Ē-…õ, ta m…ôbaŇč k…Ē nde ndaram, ta m…ôyif k…Ē yati.
\v 11 Bawo m…ôna nw…õ m…ôŇčyif k…Ē m…Ē, w…ômar k…Ēn m…ôy…Ēn…õ d…ôy…õb…ôc y…Ēn y…õl…õc.
\s1 Moloku m…õlp…ôs
\p 
\v 12 Ali nt…õ moloku m…õlar im k…ôloku nu m…Ē, ifaŇč f…õ k…ôloku nu mi d'areka Ňčecic…ôs. Mba iŇčgb…õk…ôr amera k…ôk…Ēn…ôŇčk un, ilok-lok…ôr nu pat…õf…ôr…õn…õ nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôbotu posu p…õlar…õ m…Ē.
\p 
\v 13 Awut a w…ôkir…õ kam nw…õ Kanu k…ôy…õk-y…õk m…Ē\f + \fr 1:13 \fq Awut a w…ôkir…õ kam nw…õ Kanu k…ôy…õk-y…õk m…Ē\ft = K…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč Yesu\f* Ňčayif nu.
